data.text: New York: Boni & Liveright, 1927. First printing. Hardcover. Quarto, cloth, illustrated, fair copy, owner's signature on the front flyleaf, remnants of the (lacking) dust jacket are stuck in pieces to the rear cover, wear to the covers of the book including rubbing or fraying at the tips, no dust jacket. Related 1 sheet from Boni & Liveright loosely inserted. The dust jacket's rear flap (noting Theodore Dreiser's works) also inserted. Uncommon. Fair. Item #0088724
